rComments: He is a very nice man who is passionate about his teaching and his work and shares stories about his engineering experience. He seems to answer questions in an open-ended manner and doesn't usually make class objectives clear.

he's pretty boring in the beginning with the powerpoint presentations, but as you go on he gets more interesting.  basically, just go overboard on the projects and it's a guaranteed A... and i even slept thru half the semester.
USELESS!  This guy couldn't explain a concept if his life depended on it.
